snippet.title: Cat Quest II - Official Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
The story of two kingdoms at war, and the heroes that must rise to save it.
Releasing some time in 2019!

https://www.facebook.com/catquestgame/
https://discord.gg/catquest
https://thegentlebros.com/catquest2/

Cat Quest II is an action RPG where you can play as a cat and a dog, solo or with a friend! Shedding its fur in 2019 on Switch, PS4, Xbox One, Steam, and mobile!
